26:42.000 --> 26:48.000
But I would argue it's our duty because we probably won't be here on this planet forever and the human genomes not built to live on other planets.

26:48.000 --> 26:55.000
So we may have to think of a time when we re-engineer the species on which we depend or even the human genome in order to actually survive in a long, long, long term.

26:55.000 --> 27:00.000
I think we have the ability of the species to think that far so we should consider that as a thought experiment.

27:00.000 --> 27:07.000
